&_nc_ohc=KalNN18_afkQ7kNvgF44lA3&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAwj0MnZZRKlj5jy5y0w1f98KgXNdstxJvPkd-mvK3cYw&oe=6722217E"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "142763513777212", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/12427536_253589715002993_418784534_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=yR8k5C_qtYoQ7kNvgEOhYYj&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD4Vk-1gPl99Z0OLmjnPM87w_6LMisQd1s8INupHfxx3A&oe=672215F4"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "The Presence", "keywords": ["Movie", "Film", "Horror", "Interactive", "Seance"], "long_description": "The Presence is an interactive, live-action, horror film, built for the Gear VR. The story follows four characters through a s\u00e9ance gone wrong. As the movie progresses viewers are able to affect the point of view and discover different aspects of a complex story. A proof-of-concept piece, The Presence illustrates two new approaches to VR storytelling: free roam and cinematic. In both versions, the viewer influences how the story unfolds. In the free roam version, the viewer is able to jump between multiple perspectives at will; while in the cinematic version, the viewer's gaze motivates the next shot, editing the film organically.\n\n          Additional storage required:  ~1.5GB\n          Runtime:  ~6 minutes\n\nThe Presence contains strong language and violence and is recommended for a mature audience only.\n\nThe Presence works with the Gear VR touchpad or most Bluetooth controllers.", "short_description": "The Presence is an interactive, live-action, horror film following four characters through a s\u00e9ance gone wrong. A proof-of-concept piece, The Presence illustrates two new approaches to VR storytelling: free roam and cinematic. In the free roam version, the viewer is able to jump between multiple perspectives at will; while in the cinematic version, the viewer's gaze motivates the next shot, editi